{"tid":362161,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個細個對NBA嘅誤解","createTime":"2017-08-16T17:01:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T19:06:33.000Z","uid":135744,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"664d9f9bc183c7f7889d7399a9ab701d30f45963","tid":362161,"uid":135744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T17:01:25.000Z","msg":"我講先 。。。<br />\n<br />\n小學嗰陣以為NBA球隊嘅名係反映到一隊球隊嘅特質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />例如雷霆d球員跑得好似閃電咁快，火箭會飛到好高所以有姚明，勇士嘅球員好勇敢會搏哂老命打波，而熱火嘅人就特別熱血，etc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家諗番起都on99<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家細個有冇對NBA有趣嘅誤解可以分享下呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d49717c135feaa3b8d1e795202cca235bc76b106","tid":362161,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T17:04:20.000Z","msg":"入場資格係要兩米高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70adcf68a5f51e68b7faf3da96811a2bb6cc61f3","tid":362161,"uid":41434,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T17:04:29.000Z","msg":"係運動"},{"pid":"815bbc9496446cb59cc1faab9a1498ff98c1927f","tid":362161,"uid":36851,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T17:06:20.000Z","msg":"以為個場同香港d街場一樣大"},{"pid":"127a3c8e3ece438e8b314cd9a0b3d0264274f1c4","tid":362161,"uid":102603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T17:06:23.000Z","msg":"姚明好撚廢<br />\n大個先知勁"},{"pid":"e4be31347da0a524b3b22ffa058c08efb508e3d4","tid":362161,"uid":2313,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T17:06:24.000Z","msg":"仲以為畀大人玩"},{"pid":"11d8144b0a49c3ea9d34b3e5a260da702540e79e","tid":362161,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T17:07:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>姚明好撚廢<br />\n大個先知勁</blockquote><br />\nSame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk